nodes.text: Gahseelik was a male Trandoshan who disgraced his clan by leaving Trandosha to work for Gardulla the Hutt during the waning years of the Republic Classic era. For this a bounty was posted on his head by Trossilik. His bounty was claimed by Jango Fett for 3,000 credits, who was on a mission to meet with Gardulla.
Gahseelik's bounty was worth 3,000 credits alive and 1,500 credits dead.
